      <title>野村证券利润因固定收益交易和零售繁荣而大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/nomura-rebounds-with-first-annual-profit-growth-under-ceo-okuda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司(Nomura Holdings Inc.)的盈利攀升，固定收益交易的飙升和日本市场的复苏帮助首席执行官奥田健太郎(Kentaro Okuda)在他的领导下实现了年度利润的首次增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/nomura-rebounds-with-first-annual-profit-growth-under-ceo-okuda</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 06:15:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
